islative agenda and torment his former tormenter, <strong>Donald Trump</str=
ong>. In many ways, it=E2=80=99s a fitting final act.</p><p style=3D"margin=
:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">This week, th=
