 than McConnell about the pressure each senator is under=E2=80=94weighing t=
heir own primary threats, public attacks from MAGA world, and phone calls f=
rom Trump on each vote, to name just a few. =C2=A0<br/><br/>Nevertheless, M=
cConnell is hoping to command significant sway among Senate Republicans on =
foreign policy and defense spending. As the top defense appropriator, he ha=
s told people that when he=E2=80=99s done with the defense budget, he=E2=80=
=99ll
make the late <strong>John McCain </strong>look like a dove by comparison.=
