ichael Tackett</strong>=E2=80=99s biography of McConnell, the author quotes=
 former senator <strong>Lamar Alexander</strong> as telling his subject, =
=E2=80=9CYou=E2=80=99ll always be remembered for the last thing you do.=E2=
=80=9D Now McConnell is betting his legacy on preventing Trump and his Repu=
blican followers from shrinking America=E2=80=99s role in the world. As bud=
get battles are gearing up and a faction of hardline Republicans are vowing=
 to cut the
defense budget, his first test will arrive very soon.</p></div>
